stateDiagram-v2
    %% Main States
    [*] --> NotificationsPage: User clicks Notifications icon
    
    %% Notifications Page and its components
    NotificationsPage --> UnifiedFeed: Default view

    %% Unified Feed Section
    UnifiedFeed --> NotificationItem: User clicks notification
    NotificationItem --> MarkRead: User clicks "Mark as Read" button
    MarkRead --> UnifiedFeed: Updates notification status
    
    NotificationItem --> MarkUnread: User clicks "Mark as Unread" button
    MarkUnread --> UnifiedFeed: Updates notification status
    
    NotificationItem --> DismissNotification: User clicks "Dismiss" button
    DismissNotification --> UnifiedFeed: Removes notification from active list
    
    NotificationItem --> ArchiveNotification: User clicks "Archive" button
    ArchiveNotification --> UnifiedFeed: Moves to archive list
    
    NotificationItem --> ViewDetails: User clicks "View Details" button
    ViewDetails --> RelatedContent: Navigates to source page
    RelatedContent --> NotificationsPage: User returns to notifications
    
    %% Filtering & Sorting Section
    UnifiedFeed --> FilterNotifications: User clicks "Filter" button
    FilterNotifications --> CategoryFilter: User selects category filter
    CategoryFilter --> ApplyFilters: Filter by appointment/inventory/billing
    ApplyFilters --> FilteredResults: Shows filtered notifications
    FilteredResults --> UnifiedFeed: User clears filters
    
    UnifiedFeed --> SortNotifications: User clicks "Sort" button
    SortNotifications --> SortByDate: User selects "Sort by Date"
    SortNotifications --> SortByPriority: User selects "Sort by Priority"
    SortByDate --> SortedResults: Shows date sorted notifications
    SortByPriority --> SortedResults: Shows priority sorted notifications
    SortedResults --> UnifiedFeed: User clears sorting
    
    %% Notification Settings
    NotificationsPage --> NotificationSettings: User clicks "Settings" button
    NotificationSettings --> CategorySettings: Configure notification categories 
    CategorySettings --> ToggleAppointmentNotifs: Toggle appointment notifications
    CategorySettings --> ToggleInventoryNotifs: Toggle inventory notifications
    CategorySettings --> ToggleBillingNotifs: Toggle billing notifications
    
    NotificationSettings --> ChannelSettings: Configure notification channels
    ChannelSettings --> ToggleInAppNotifs: Toggle in-app notifications
    ChannelSettings --> ToggleEmailNotifs: Toggle email notifications
    
    ToggleAppointmentNotifs --> SaveSettings: User saves changes
    ToggleInventoryNotifs --> SaveSettings: User saves changes
    ToggleBillingNotifs --> SaveSettings: User saves changes
    ToggleInAppNotifs --> SaveSettings: User saves changes
    ToggleEmailNotifs --> SaveSettings: User saves changes
    
    SaveSettings --> NotificationsPage: Return to notifications with updated settings
    
    %% Archived Notifications
    NotificationsPage --> ArchivedNotifications: User clicks "View Archived" button
    ArchivedNotifications --> ArchivedItem: User clicks archived notification
    ArchivedItem --> RestoreNotification: User clicks "Restore" button
    RestoreNotification --> ArchivedNotifications: Removes from archive list
    ArchivedItem --> DeleteNotification: User clicks "Delete" button
    DeleteNotification --> ArchivedNotifications: Permanently removes notification
    ArchivedNotifications --> NotificationsPage: User returns to active notifications
    
    %% Real-time Alert Mechanism
    NotificationsPage --> RealTimeAlert: New critical notification arrives
    RealTimeAlert --> AlertPopup: Shows popup with notification details
    AlertPopup --> ViewAlertDetails: User clicks "View" button
    ViewAlertDetails --> RelatedContent: Navigates to source page
    AlertPopup --> DismissAlert: User clicks "Dismiss" button
    DismissAlert --> NotificationsPage: Closes popup, notification still in feed
    
    %% Style Definitions
    classDef primary fill:#2563eb,stroke:#1e40af,color:white
    classDef secondary fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#2563eb,color:white
    classDef action fill:#34d399,stroke:#10b981,color:black
    classDef alert fill:#ef4444,stroke:#b91c1c,color:white
    
    %% Apply Styles
    class NotificationsPage,UnifiedFeed,NotificationSettings,ArchivedNotifications primary
    class NotificationItem,FilterNotifications,SortNotifications,CategorySettings,ChannelSettings,ArchivedItem secondary
    class MarkRead,MarkUnread,DismissNotification,ArchiveNotification,ViewDetails,SaveSettings,RestoreNotification,DeleteNotification action
    class RealTimeAlert,AlertPopup alert